<A>__{but as he speaks the last words, sidney's voice falters because he has glanced down at the table...}
<B>__{sidney}
<A>__{we see that an idea has entered his head an idea that takes the wind out of his indignation. his eyes lift rapidly to hunsecker's face.}
<C>__{hunsecker}
