<A>__{camera shoots across sidney again onto hunsecker. hunsecker leans back, looks at sidney. seeing that sidney has accepted the proposition, he smiles.}
<C>__{hunsecker}
<P>__{(softly)}
<D>__{thank you, sidney.}
<A>__{in a pleasantly affable way, he leans across the table to tap the hand with which sidney is leaning on the table.}
<C>__{hunsecker}
<D>__{and, sidney, i will have that piece of paper back...}
<A>__{helplessly, sidney unclenches a fist and reveals the slip of paper which he had meant to keep. hunsecker takes it. with his eyes on sidney, he slowly tears it up...}
